ENAITURUK

Ore embuku oo LAIGUANAK le dukuya naa enkatini nalo dukuya te nkitoria e Israel anaa pee eiteruni te mbuku e Samuel. Eidimi aatoor ena buku katitin uni. (
1  ) Pee eng'amaa Solomon enkitoria e Israel o Yuda o keeya e papaai lenye Daudi. (
2  ) Enkitoria o dupoto naanoto Solomon. Ore embae sapuk naibala naa enchetata e nkaji Enkai te Yerusalem. (
3  ) Etooroki olosho le Israel aaitaa nkitoriat are, aa enkitoria e enkalo e moikuape o enkitoria e nkalo e kopikop o nkatinin oo laiguanak ooitoria ninche o metabaiki ilarin iip naaudo o onom. (B.C.)

Ore te pooki buku oo laiguanak, neiguanareki ake pooki aiguanani te uriata enye Enkai, naa ore enkisulata olosho nelioo te nkisiligata eina uriata e Nkai. Ore pee eserem inkitanyaanyukot oo nkaitin negolong'u nepuo aaidaaya ninche. Ore ilaiguanak pooki le nkitoria e moikuape, netabatatate pooki teina temata, ore enkitoria e Yuda neitu ebatata pooki.

Ore ilooibala oleng loo laiguanak le dukuya naa iloibonok le Nkai, lelo oibonok oogol oishuaa ooiro te rishata e Nkai eikok iltung'ana peyie meomon inkitanyaanyukot oo nkaitin nemeany eanyit Enkai. Ore oloibala oleng naa Eliya otigilunore ilapolosak le Baal. (
